            (m) P.-O. STRINDBERG (m) INGRID SUNDBERG (m) ALF WENNERFORS (m)
            ANDERS WIJKMAN (m)
          </p>
          <p xml:id="i-L1gsBDgUNfPBoynzMQk4VC">
            TORE NILSSON (m) i Agnäs
          </p>
